 In this food vlog, Sisi Yemmie shares how to make ekuru and ekuru Sauce and she hopes you like this recipe. Ekuru is also known as White Moin Moin, some call it Ofuloju and it is so delicious. Dedicated to Nigerian food and recipes, Sisi Yemmie is a food and lifestyle blogger documenting bits of every other day in her life with her son Tito, daughter Tiara and husband. Watch the vlog below:   The best Nigerian and African video content from around the web specially curated for YOU! 